     A free-roaming squad based RPG. Focusing on open-ended gameplay features
   rather than a linear story. Be a trader, a thief, a rebel, a mercenary, a
   business owner, a doctor, a bandit... the list goes on. Aid or oppose the
   various factions in the world while striving for the strength and wealth
   necessary to simply survive in the harsh desert. Purchase and upgrade your
   own buildings to use as safe fortified havens when things go bad, or use
   them to start up a business. Train your men up from puny victims to master
   warriors. Carry your wounded squad mates to safety and get them all home
   alive.
